column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/p4649_b197bf3270490068319d87e4b977b08f754a1307/ for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-te
Please check trayIconMenu for 0 here. It may still be 0 if a setClientModel(0) is done but never a setClientModel(somethingelse).\n
